Ing '''langis''' o '''linasa''' (''Sesamum indicum''), a '''sesame''' king Ingles, metung yang [[tanaman a manyampaga]] (''flowering plant'') king genus a ''[[Sesamum]]''. Dakal ya kamaganak a tutubu king ilang king Africa ampong mas ditak a bilang king India. [[naturalization (biology)|Naturalisadu]] ne o tutubung e mitanam kareng dakal a labuad a malisangan o tropical a labuad kareng miayaliwang dake ning yatu, at tatanam de para kareng butul nang kakanan, a makabili kareng pods anti king bule o kamangyang.

Metung ya ing langis kareng pekamatwang tatanam a butul a pikukuanan laru a balu ra king yatu, at tatanam de maygit atlung libu nang (3000) banwa ing milabas. Pilan da neng libung banwang manimunang mitatanam neng kaleldo king [[Kalibudtang Aslagan]] (''Middle East''), agpang kareng atuklasan dang panapsal laru king labuad a iti.<ref>[http://www.haaretz.com/weekend/pleasure-hunting/.premium-1.543039 Open Sesame, [[Haaretz]]]</ref> Agyu ning langis ing kumabyeng malwat neng maki [[lawi]] o panaun ning malambat a pangalangi, at tutubu ya neng mangamate no reng dakal a tanam.<ref name=rram/><ref name=drl2/>

Metung ya kareng dakal dila laru kareng butul ing langis. Uli ning kayang malinamnam a lasang kawangis ning mani, maralas deng gagamitan king pamaglutu kareng dakal a dake ning yatu.<ref name=rhan/><ref name=esopl/> Kalupa de reng aliwang nues o ''nuts'' ampong pamangan a magdalang [[allergy]] kareng aliwang tau.<ref name=simsim1/>

